query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci k mk n t) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci k mk n t kt) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci k kt mk n t chn) */ select min(t.title) AS complete_downey_ironman_movie
from name AS n
inner join cast_info AS ci
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.name like '%Roversi,%'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('web',
'marvel-comics',
'sequel',
'based-on-comic',
'female-nudity',
'sequel',
'laser',
'number-in-title')
inner join complete_cast AS cc
on mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind like '%complete%'
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1996
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name not like '%Sherlock%' AND chn.name like '%Rondón%';
